---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Claude Code Workshop | tcplot(Data Visualization Twin Cities)"
    description="AI-assisted coding workshop for data visualization practitioners using Claude Code."
>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Upcoming: Claude Code for Data Visualization — May 23rd
            </h2>

            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                AI-assisted coding is changing how visualization practitioners
                prototype, iterate, and ship. In this hands-on workshop, we'll
                get you up and running with Claude Code — Anthropic's agentic
                coding tool — and put it to work on real dataviz problems. No
                prior experience with AI coding tools required.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Whether you're deep in D3, grinding through ggplot2, or
                somewhere in between, you'll leave with a working setup and a
                concrete sense of where Claude Code fits (and doesn't fit) in a
                practitioner's workflow.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                Location & Logistics
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="mt-1 text-gray-400">&#x25B8;</span>
                    <span
                        ><strong class="text-gray-900">When:</strong> Saturday, May
                        23 · 10:00 AM to 12:00 PM CDT</span
                    >
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="mt-1 text-gray-400">&#x25B8;</span>
                    <span
                        ><strong class="text-gray-900">Where:</strong> The Coffee
                        Shop NE, 2852 Johnson St NE, Minneapolis, MN</span
                    >
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="mt-1 text-gray-400">&#x25B8;</span>
                    <span>Make sure to bring your laptop and charger.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
                <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                        src="/images/claudecode1.png"
                        alt="Claude Code terminal running in front of a Stanford Torus space habitat with lush gardens"
                        class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                        src="/images/claudecode2.png"
                        alt="Claude Code terminal running in front of the Tereshkova space station"
                        class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
